<title>yạ ʿjbaⁿạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ʿjbaⁿạ mkẖlṣy qd mạt mn ạ̉jly
 wsfk ạldm ạlzky fdy̱ lkẖạṭỷ mtẖly
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉ḥbny rby nʿm ạ̉ḥbny
